title: American Horror Stories 01x03 Scenes Pack || Rabbit Rabbit

comment: I saw the third episode of American Horror Stories just last night, and I think it's better than the first two episodes.  Don't get me wrong, they were good episodes as well.  But somehow I prefer the third one over its predecessors.
